      "versionNonce": 274,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Container crash recovery\n\nWho detects a crashed / OOM-killed container and replaces it?\n  \u2022  Docker's own --restart policy?\n  \u2022  A health-check loop in the orchestrator polling /health?\n\nNeither is specified anywhere in AGENT_RUNTIME_ARCHITECTURE.md \u00a75.\n\u2192 Needs an explicit decision before Phase 1 ships.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Container crash recovery\n\nWho detects a crashed / OOM-killed container and replaces it?\n  \u2022  Docker's own --restart policy?\n  \u2022  A health-check loop in the orchestrator polling /health?\n\nNeither is specified anywhere in AGENT_RUNTIME_ARCHITECTURE.md \u00a75.\n\u2192 Needs an explicit decision before Phase 1 ships.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "o_q2_88",
