      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Data on crash \u2014 kept or lost?\n\nControl-plane data (task/run history, agent metadata) lives in\nPostgres \u2014 survives a container crash fine, see \u00a78 above.\n\nBut in-flight task state / workspace files (Week 6's file_write\nsandbox) live inside the CONTAINER's own filesystem. Volume-\nmounted and recoverable, or gone with the container? Undecided.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Data on crash \u2014 kept or lost?\n\nControl-plane data (task/run history, agent metadata) lives in\nPostgres \u2014 survives a container crash fine, see \u00a78 above.\n\nBut in-flight task state / workspace files (Week 6's file_write\nsandbox) live inside the CONTAINER's own filesystem. Volume-\nmounted and recoverable, or gone with the container? Undecided.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 10
    },
