      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. Customer BYO (AWS / GCP) \u2014 partially answered\n\nPhase 3's Runner pattern (\u2191 above) DOES answer \"can a customer\nrun this in their own AWS/GCP\" \u2014 that part exists.\n\nWhat it doesn't answer: do Q1 (crash recovery) and Q2 (data\npersistence) work the same way inside the customer's own cloud,\nor does their infra handle it differently? Not specified.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. Customer BYO (AWS / GCP) \u2014 partially answered\n\nPhase 3's Runner pattern (\u2191 above) DOES answer \"can a customer\nrun this in their own AWS/GCP\" \u2014 that part exists.\n\nWhat it doesn't answer: do Q1 (crash recovery) and Q2 (data\npersistence) work the same way inside the customer's own cloud,\nor does their infra handle it differently? Not specified.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 10
    },
